reuo.client
Class Request<T>

java.lang.Object
  reuo.client.Request<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The response type; this is what will satisfy the response (see resolve(Object))
Direct Known Subclasses:
AccountHandler.LoginRequest, AccountHandler.ShardRequest, TargetRequest
public abstract class Request<T>
extends Object

An abstract respresenting a request to be satisified or cancelled. Requests end once they are cancelled and cannot be satisfied. Likewise, Requests that are satisfied end and cannot be cancelled. The isOpen() method will check if the request is still valid.
